Mesh upper: the upper offers targeted support, flexibility, and ventilation, promoting optimal airflow. This minimizes sweat buildup, ensuring a comfortable and breathable experience for your feet.

Lace up: the laces create a comprehensive and even distribution of pressure across the foot and also provides a secure and stable feel.

Cushioned comfort: enjoy plush comfort with a pu foam insole, responsive support from an eva midsole.

Shock absorption: the eva outsole effectively dampens shocks, minimizing stress on the feet and joints, and reducing the risk of discomfort or injury during play.
